---
---

<header class="header">
  <span class="eyebrow">Featured Collections</span>

  <h2>Crafted For Every Celebration</h2>

  <p>
    Discover signature couture collections designed to celebrate every
    unforgettable moment.
  </p>
</header>

<style>
  .header {
    display: grid;
    justify-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    max-width: var(--measure-md);
    margin: 0 auto clamp(var(--space-8), 6vw, var(--space-11));
    text-align: center;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    color: var(--cocoa-400);
    font-size: var(--caption);
    font-weight: var(--weight-semibold);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-label);
    line-height: var(--leading-caption);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4.5vw, 4.75rem);
    font-weight: var(--weight-light);
    line-height: var(--leading-heading);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-heading);
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  p {
    max-width: var(--measure-xs);
    margin-inline: auto;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--body-md);
    line-height: var(--leading-body);
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .header {
      justify-items: start;
      gap: var(--space-3);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-7);
      text-align: left;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 12vw, 3.25rem);
    }
  }
</style>
